kgmoji\" /> <br />\n你仲覺得無問題呀？<br />\n你個腦俾屎忽坐著左呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成班小學雞成日講咩道德撚 食花生 根本連對與錯都唔識分就係到話人 不知所謂"},{"pid":"bf22ba9343fed088208915040bdeaf8ec73c2ea6","tid":31944,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"釣厹呢個行為本身唔覺有問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過人地做完一次成班又跟風走去做真係好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d392b6c348b5e25c43b376f4f9b4318b4f09f2d8","tid":31944,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"咁主動引班狗公又唔係咁好<br />\n係釣都要等佢地自己主動先"},{"pid":"a9f5972b45161367a19912f6a9f2d8c17a53b600","tid":31944,"uid":1294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>釣厹呢個行為本身唔覺有問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過人地做完一次成班又跟風走去做真係好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係想表達出呢樣野 成班人睇又唔睇我打乜 一又反對聲音就屌左先 又亂咁批評人係道德撚 而家唔係人多就係真理岩曬囉"},{"pid":"5b0bbcadd85674aa3ffb5282db746d9551bed143","tid":31944,"uid":1294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁主動引班狗公又唔係咁好<br />\n係釣都要等佢地自己主動先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩呀 如果今次件事係好似beatbox仔七次鳩痕主動約人扑野 我都推埋一份 但而家原全唔係 有錯就要屌都好正常"},{"pid":"cf25957ed6538eeb64b1f1bbad000387c5cb1314","tid":31944,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:34:49.000Z","msg":"條NewAge死撚左呀？<br />\n蒲頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147225409ea72d0acbce98ad3864617e977cf96c","tid":31944,"uid":28393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"咁得閒 比心機溝女算啦<br />\n 係度扮女人裝人彈弓 係咪心裡唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888d0651a76e37fdaf730c9a73b747d056632769","tid":31944,"uid":19421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 周瑜子宮緊 )<br />